Comment: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:23.23,Ristorante,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The People of the Ristorante

Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:05.23,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's time to go and try it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Your food for the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.60,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:13.35,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not ready to serve it to the owner yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Stop at a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:20.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Staying up late is bad for your complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:22.16,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:34.36,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this looks like a cinch to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.85,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Was that pot there before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:43.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure feels good to do a nice deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:45.11,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It was {\i1}her{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:49.56,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Every once in a while she does something that reminds me she's my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.39,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:23.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot that {\i1}her{\i0} birthday's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.75,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,We had a party for her here last year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.94,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Did you receive an invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.25,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:35.97,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:41.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Since she doesn't want the owner to know that I'm actually her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:45.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she had no choice but to invite me this year, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.60,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,because I came to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.94,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the case at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:54.83,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's delighted to be able to spend her special day with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.81,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:02:59.49,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.55,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Is nine o'clock OK for Gabrielle's reservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.49,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.30,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I should get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.59,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for preparing the antipasto for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:32.25,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Claudio and Luciano were the ones behind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.11,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be awaiting your next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.96,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She shouldn't even come to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.82,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's just going to annoy Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:57.14,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Be more gentle with the ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:02.12,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,There are seven parties booked for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.94,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}One of them is a group from Japan, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:07.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio said he didn't feel that way anymore, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:10.14,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That ring barely stays on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.78,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you haven't lost weight, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.24,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My fingers have gotten narrower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Why not just take the ring off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.76,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,We've been through this before, Vito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.03,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he can't forget those memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.83,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.95,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's déjà vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.50,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that he can't forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.80,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,it's that he doesn't want to forget, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.51,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.92,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that like it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.35,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nicoletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.26,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they sure are late...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.99,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,May I interrupt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.03,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Nicoletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.62,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,This is your dress for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.49,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I just finished buying it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.05,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.88,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I took the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.79,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.81,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,One cappuccino, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.72,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Should I give you two a few minutes to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.61,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I have to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.10,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.64,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.82,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I think you know how Claudio feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.56,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That's all in the past. There's nothing to discuss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:59.88,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe for you, but not for Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.65,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,And don't tell me you haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:08.49,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the restaurant all the time, even when you know how he feels, is downright cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.36,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:22.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.26,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:27.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.35,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,can I still come by once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.41,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The food is just so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:44.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows Nicoletta has a crush on Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.59,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.76,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Think about Claudio's feelings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.38,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:52.43,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.93,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.20,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Though,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.86,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,you really should take the ring off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.88,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to hate myself for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.11,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Luciano is so blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.02,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio! Gabrielle's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.04,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a break from the restaurant for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.54,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Want to meet and talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.45,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:25.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That red-headed girl stopped by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.02,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nicoletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.54,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She said it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:37.05,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That it's cruel for me to go to the restaurant when I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.56,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.06,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.60,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:50.52,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She really cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.98,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What's so wrong with making Claudio some pasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:01.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, come try this dress on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.10,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What's that pot all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:08.14,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really. I was just in a cooking mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio seemed to really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:10.87,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.93,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He keeps a close eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:18.75,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I think he was impressed at how you approached Gabrielle earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.45,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:27.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,To think you grew up so well even with me not being around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I really owe it to your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.53,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:39.07,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's almost spring here in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.41,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still cold there, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.12,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But forget that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:48.97,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about Olga's birthday party coming up. You're going, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:53.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's so random. She's never invited me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.77,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Just forgive her and let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.77,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She thought of you in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.18,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:08.44,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Every year she'd send me a letter saying how sorry she was for not inviting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:13.74,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to get her, Luciano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.20,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna ask that and not say what you're getting her yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.79,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Have a cup of coffee, Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.32,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.83,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,A list of those invited to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.21,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be purely a guest tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.80,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm going to be in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:39.26,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The Madam will be happier to see you attending as her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,A daughter of a close friend, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.14,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Claudio know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.97,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't wearing the dress I picked out for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:51.64,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a staff member...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:54.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,All the men are going to be wearing suits tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.07,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,so I think it's OK if you wear a formal dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.53,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing a dress in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.41,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Teo's not gonna like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. You'll take the day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:07.60,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cozy party only for close friends and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:10.71,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she'll be coming too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.77,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.59,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Gabrielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.17,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Doubtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:26.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I peeked at the menu before, and it looks fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Go tell her she should come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's your good friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.46,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Nicoletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.41,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good girl, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.84,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:47.11,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a big party here for her birthday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.79,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always so busy in November...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:56.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I've only ever been able to send a present and a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:00.21,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad she could be here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:04.70,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it'd be bad if others found out that she's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:08.54,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Your ring looks like it's going to come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:14.68,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You should wear a different ring, if it's just to keep the customers at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.36,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.07,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:23.77,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You make it so easy to take advantage of you, Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.16,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.51,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.08,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:32.80,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Gabrielle isn't the only one waiting for you to take that ring off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.12,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Is my hair going to be OK all flat like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.30,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:44.72,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:52.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she just cooked it for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:59.65,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, can she even cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:03.66,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I can't picture her acting like a housewife...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.46,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:41.51,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You look concerned about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.69,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.41,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:52.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll the keep the fact I'm your daughter a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The food is a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:04.74,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fantastic? Gigi's eating his fill tonight, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:07.97,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,And we've got extra help tonight, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.16,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm honored to be standing in the same kitchen as Mr. Facchini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.48,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,As you're a guest tonight, you are not to enter the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.64,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to block me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:20.88,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He's blushing because you look so fetching tonight, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.49,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You're always quick with the jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:28.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But she truly is fetching. Don't you agree, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.82,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:36.10,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Teo, it's about time we bring her dish to the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.00,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Carry it out, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:41.58,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What? I-I shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:44.23,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're so modest all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:46.83,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was trying to pay you your rightful dues.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.88,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.66,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best meal you've made so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.35,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You did a proper job and put feeling into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.85,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Show some more confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.03,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:12.08,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you ask someone else to do it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:16.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.08,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's got it together so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.37,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it's not because you didn't raise her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:23.42,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:27.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to be one of the worst mothers alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}were{\i0} one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.97,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But now, she's close by and really looks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:37.27,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,A girl moving on from her mother is a huge deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:41.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to become a charming lady right by your side now, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:49.09,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Tanti auguri a te.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.59,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Tanti auguri a te.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.04,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Lorenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:57.00,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Tanti auguri a Olga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:01.17,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Tanti auguri a te.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.96,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,My, it looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:06.58,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nicoletta made this cake for you. She said it's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.87,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I have a confession to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:39.26,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter, Nicoletta, made this cake for me as a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:39.95,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.83,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I had her with my ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:49.15,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for keeping it secret all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.66,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to be rejected,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.80,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,so I just kept on lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.58,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.81,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:06.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she was your daughter soon after she started working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You have the same smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why you never said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:15.41,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But, Lorenzo, you said you don't like women with kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.77,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'd have preferred that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:24.04,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'll welcome her with open arms, if she's your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:42.48,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.78,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I just get to be a selfish brat for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:49.82,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, blow out the candles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.52,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.28,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll carry those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.68,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That was anticlimactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:44.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think the owner was the type to reject her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.11,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,and turns out I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:51.31,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But, I also understand what it's like to be a woman frantically in love and afraid of rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.30,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be rejected either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:17:59.30,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You're in luck, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.46,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:34.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Olga really seems like she's made up for lost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:37.23,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's like revealing her daughter has given her new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:39.05,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,How are things at the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.51,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,She's continuing on as an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.97,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Luciano still scolds her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.89,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to see me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.24,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.24,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Have you responded to her feelings for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.17,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:10.16,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:12.88,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,We're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.27,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Come by the restaurant sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.73,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here's a little extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Claudio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.02,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.50,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,No way, my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.83,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:41.74,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nicoletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.80,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, she misspoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.56,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out shopping too, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:50.34,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll carry your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.17,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.21,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else you want to check out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.72,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:05.60,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I usually relax at home on my days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.21,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.56,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you something good to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:13.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Carry those bags to my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:25.16,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the regulars will be able to tell we're an item.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:29.40,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I won somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.50,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,OK, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:46.67,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is casetta dell'orso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:51.98,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in Rome, go look for it...
